name: Sabine Kvenberg
what_you_do: Sabine Kvenberg is a keynote speaker, bestselling author, and founder of Impact Communication Coaching. She helps leaders, entrepreneurs, and teams master 'The Invisible Stage™' - the unseen moments of preparation and everyday conversations where influence is won or lost.
social_proof: Sabine is a bestselling author and has decades of experience working with people from all walks of life to overcome their fear of public speaking.
signature_programs: Gumption (book), Confident Speaker Accelerator, Camera Confidence
business_focus: Helping entrepreneurs and business professionals improve their communication skills and become empowered so they can grow their businesses and transform lives.
service_provided: One-on-One Coaching, Group Workshops, Webinars and Online Courses
